<title>Parabolas</title>
<introduction>
<table>
<tabular>
<row>
<cell><p>By the end of this section, you should</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>know the geometric definition of a parabola.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>know the meaning of vertex, focus, directrix, and axis of a parabola.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>be able to find equation of a parabola whose axis is horizontal or vertical.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>be able to identify equations representing sec-parabolas.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>be able to find the vertex, focus, and directrix of a parabola and sketch the parabola.</p>
</li>
</ul></cell>
</row>
</tabular>
</table>

</introduction>

